<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
      i18n:domain="rosetta">

<body>

<div metal:fill-slot="main" tal:define="submitted view/requestProjectSubmit">

    <div tal:condition="submitted">
        <div tal:condition="view/error">
            <h1>Error</h1>

            <p>
            There was an error sending the request message.
            <p>

            <p>
            Details: <code tal:content="view/error">blah blah blah</code>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div tal:condition="not: view/error">
            <h1>Request Sent</h1>

            <p>
            Your project request has been sent for review.
            </p>

            <p>
            <a tal:attributes="href request/URL">Request Another Project</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h1>Request project for translation</h1>

    <p class="documentDescription">
    Please give us some information about the project you would like to
    have available for translation in Rosetta. Information such as a
    homepage URL and revision control systems details is useful.
    </p>

    <form method="POST" tal:attributes="action request/URL">
    <fieldset>
        <p>
        <label>Name</label> <input type="text" name="name" />
        </p>

        <p>
        <label>Project Homepage</label>
            <input type="text" name="homepage" size="50" />
        </p>

        <p>
        <label>Project Download Page</label>
            <input type="text" name="download-page" size="50" />
        </p>

        <p>
        <label>Description</label>
        </p>

        <p>
        In your description, please include several paragraphs about the intent
        of the project, the history of the project and major features and
        highlights of the software involved.
        </p>

        <textarea name="description" rows="15"></textarea>

        <p>
        <label>Revision Control Information</label>
        </p>

        <p>
        Please give details of any CVS/Subversion/Arch/etc. repositories the
        project has.
        </p>

        <textarea name="revision-control-info" rows="5"></textarea>

        <br/>
        <input type="submit" name="SUBMIT" value="Submit" />
    </fieldset>
    </form>

</div>

</body>
</html>
